ray%20Gade%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20rape%20of%20the%2026-year-old%20woman%2C%20ended%20in%20his%20arrest%20after%20a%2075-hour%20chase%20late%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20launched%20a%20massive%20search%20for%20Gade%2C%20deploying%20drones%20and%2013%20police%20teams%20comprising%20over%20100%20personnel%20across%20Pune%20district%20and%20beyond.%20A%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20he%20arrived%20at%20the%20house%20of%20a%20relative%20at%2010%3A30%20pm%20on%20Thursday.%20His%20relatives%2C%20upon%20learning%20of%20his%20arrival%2C%20alerted%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20leaving%2C%20Gade%20took%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%20and%20reportedly%20admitted%20to%20his%20family%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20made%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20surrender.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20team%20discovered%20a%20changed%20shirt%2C%20which%20they%20used%20to%20provide%20the%20dog%20squad%20with%20Gade's%20scent.%20The%20dogs%20led%20the%20police%20along%20his%20escape%20route.%20Gade%20hid%20in%20a%20sugarcane%20field%20near%20a%20canal%20close%20to%20his%20relatives'%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20it%20was%20the%20villagers%20who%20found%20Gade%20in%20the%20canal.%20Once%20they%20identified%20him%2C%20police%20swiftly%20took%20him%20into%20custody.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20was%20transported%20directly%20to%20Pune%2C%20where%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20of%20Swargate%20Police%20Station%20formally%20arrested%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Serial%20Offender%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGade%2C%20a%2037-year-old%20man%20from%20Pune%20district's%20Shirur%2C%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20criminal%20activities.%20There%20are%20six%20registered%20cases%20against%20him%20across%20different%20police%20stations%2C%20including%20Shirur%20and%20Shikarpur%20in%20the%20Ahilyanagar%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20criminal%20history%20dates%20back%20to%20at%20least%202019%20when%20he%20took%20a%20loan%20to%20buy%20a%20four-wheeler%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20operate%20as%20an%20informal%20taxi%20on%20the%20Pune-Ahilyanagar%20route.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20he%20lured%20elderly%20women%20into%20his%20car%2C%20feigning%20kindness%20before%20robbing%20them.%20His%20arrest%20at%20that%20time%20led%20to%20the%20recovery%20of%20approximately%20140%20grams%20(12%20tola)%20of%20stolen%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20was%20convicted%20of%20robbery%20in%20Karde%20Ghat%20near%20Shirur%2C%20serving%20a%20jail%20sentence%20of%20five%20to%20six%20months.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20released%2C%20and%20multiple%20other%20cases%20against%20him%20remained%20pending.%20These%20include%20two%20cases%20in%20Shikarpur%2C%20and%20one%20each%20in%20Supa%2C%20Kedgaon%2C%20and%20Kotwali%20police%20stations%20of%20Ahilyanagar%20district.%20Despite%20these%20records%2C%20Gade%20has%20remained%20out%20on%20bail%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20criminal%20activities%2C%20Gade%20was%20also%20politically%20active.%20He%20worked%20for%20a%20prominent%20political%20leader%20during%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20several%20photos%20of%20him%20with%20this%20leader%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20ran%20for%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Sangharsh-Mukti%20Samiti%20of%20Gunat%20village%20but%20was%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Crime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGade%20frequently%20loitered%20around%20the%20Swargate%20bus%20depot%2C%20often%20presenting%20himself%20as%20a%20police%20officer.%20CCTV%20footage%20confirmed%20that%20he%20was%20wearing%20a%20formal%20shirt%2C%20pants%2C%20and%20shoes%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20he%20even%20introduced%20himself%20as%20a%20police%20officer%20while%20speaking%20to%20the%20rape%20survivor%2C%20giving%20her%20a%20false%20name%20during%20their%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20victim%2C%20a%20working%20woman%20in%20the%20medical%20field%2C%20was%20waiting%20for%20a%20bus%20to%20Phaltan%20in%20Satara%20district%20at%20Swargate%20bus%20station%20around%205%3A45%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%20Gade%20approached%20her%2C%20addressing%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Bdidi%26quot%3B%20(sister)%20and%20falsely%20claiming%20that%20her%20bus%20was%20parked%20at%20a%20different%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20led%20her%20to%20an%20empty%20Shiv%20Shahi%20AC%20bus%2C%20convincing%20her%20that%20it%20was%20the%20right%20one.%20As%20she%20hesitated%20to%20board%20the%20darkened%20vehicle%2C%20he%20reassured%20her%2C%20only%20to%20follow%20her%20inside%20and%20commit%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20across%20Maharashtra.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20that%20the%20government%20would%20push%20for%20the%20maximum%20possible%20punishment%20for%20Gade%2C%20including%20capital%20punishment.%20Shiv%20Sena%20MLA%20Nilesh%20Rane%20even%20suggested%20reviving%20police%20%26quot%3Bencounter%20squads%26quot%3B%20to%20deal%20with%20repeat%20offenders.%20The%20Pune%20police%20had%20earlier%20announced%20a%20Rs%201%20lakh%20reward%20for%20any%20information%20leading%20to%20Gade's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20rape%20laws%20in%20India.%20Former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-bus-stand-rape-case-dy-chandrachud-nirbhaya-delhi-gangrape-remember-nirbhaya-asks-dy-chandrachud-7807215%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDY%20Chandrachud%20even%20cited%20the%20%26quot%3BNirbhaya%26quot%3B%20case%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20brutal%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20woman%20inside%20a%20bus%20in%20Delhi%20in%202012%20that%20led%20to%20nationwide%20protests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20changes%20were%20made%20in%20the%20laws%20following%20the%20'Nirbhaya'%20incident%2C%20however%2C%20we%20can%20not%20prevent%20such%20incident%20by%20only%20having%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20chief%20justice%20said%20yesterday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20Transport%20Minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik%20ordered%20a%20security%20audit%20of%20all%20bus%20depots%20across%20the%20state.%20He%20also%20directed%20that%20all%20unauthorised%20buses%20and%20vehicles%20seized%20by%20transport%20authorities%20be%20removed%20from%20depots%20by%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarnaik%20called%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20more%20female%20security%20guards%20at%20bus%20stands%2C%20citing%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20women%20passengers.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20proposed%20the%20appointment%20of%20an%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20to%20the%20vacant%20post%20of%20Chief%20Security%20and%20Vigilance%20Officer%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(MSRTC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20public%20anger%2C%20Mr%20Sarnaik%20also%20launched%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20against%20the%20Assistant%20Transport%20Superintendent%20and%20the%20Bus%20Depot%20Manager%20at%20Swargate%2C%20holding%20them%20accountable%20for%20security%20lapses%20that%20enabled%20such%20an%20incident%20to%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740725100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fqqtn5k5g_dattatray-gade-pune-bus-rape-accused-_625x300_28_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdattatray-shinde-drones-dog-hunt-a-shirt-change-how-pune-bus-rape-accused-was-hunted-down-7812798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20change%20of%20shirts%20was%20enough%20for%20the%20dog%20squad%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20smell%20and%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20location%20of%20the%20man%20accused%20of%20r