%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maha%20Kumbh%202025%20Concludes%3A%20When%20And%20Where%20Will%20The%20Next%20Kumbh%20Take%20Place%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Mela%202025%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20religious%20gatherings%2C%20concluded%20on%20Wednesday%20after%2045%20days%20of%20celebration%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20year%2C%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20set%20a%20new%20record%20for%20almost%2066%20crore%20devotees%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam%2C%20the%20confluence%20of%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20the%20mythical%20Saraswati.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20hosted%20twice%20as%20many%20pilgrims%20as%20the%20population%20of%20the%20US%2C%20which%20was%20around%2034%20crore.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20is%20the%20next%20Kumbh%20Mela%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20next%20Kumbh%20Mela%20will%20be%20held%20in%202027%20in%20Nashik%2C%20Maharashtra.%20The%20religious%20event%20will%20be%20held%20at%20Trimbakeshwar%2C%20approximately%2038%20km%20from%20Nashik.%20The%20city%20is%20located%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Godavari%20River%2C%20the%20second-longest%20river%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20also%20home%20to%20the%20Trimbakeshwar%20Shiva%20Temple%2C%20one%20of%20the%20twelve%20Jyotirlingas.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Kumbh%20Mela%202027%20will%20take%20place%20from%20July%2017%20to%20August%2017.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpeaking%20at%20the%20NASSCOM%20Technology%20and%20Leadership%20Forum%202025%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20outlined%20ambitious%20plans%20to%20integrate%20cutting-edge%20technology%20into%20the%202027%20Nashik%20Kumbh%20Mela.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20said%20technology%20would%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20enabling%20those%20unable%20to%20bathe%20in%20the%20holy%20water%20to%20experience%20it%20virtually.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20next%20Kumbh%20Mela%20in%20just%20three%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKumbh%20Melas%20are%20held%20in%20four%20cities%20--%20Prayagraj%2C%20Haridwar%2C%20Nashik%2C%20and%20Ujjain%20--%20with%20at%20least%20one%20organised%20every%20three%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20one%20held%20every%20four%20years%20is%20called%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20while%20the%20fair%20that%20takes%20place%20every%20six%20years%20is%20called%20Ardh%20Kumbh%20Mela.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20mela%2C%20conducted%20every%2012%20years%2C%20is%20called%20Purna%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20and%20the%20just%20concluded%20one%20was%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20which%20is%20said%20to%20occur%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20144%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Highlights%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Mela%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMaha%20Kumbh%20Mela%202025%20attracted%20numerous%20figures%2C%20including%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20UP%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Gujarat%20CM%20Bhupendrabhai%20Patel%2C%20business%20tycoons%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVarious%20Bollywood%20celebrities%2C%20including%20Akshay%20Kumar%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20and%20Vicky%20Kaushal%2C%20also%20attended%20the%20religious%20event.%20The%20lead%20singer%20of%20Coldplay%2C%20Chris%20Martin%2C%20also%20marked%20his%20presence%20at%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20least%20118%20diplomats%20from%2077%20countries%20attended%20the%20religious%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740723000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvduechrg_maha-kumbh-prayagraj_625x300_26_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaha-kumbh-2025-concludes-when-and-where-the-next-gathering-will-be-7813054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Mela%202025%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20religious%20gatherings%2C%20concluded%20