0not%20only%20baseless%20but%20also%20reeks%20of%20ignorance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20further%20stated%20that%20while%20there%20is%20an%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Information%20Technology%20(IIIT)%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20the%20institute%20had%20confirmed%20that%20it%20had%20never%20invited%20Mr%20Pitroda%20to%20any%20conference%20or%20seminar%2C%20whether%20physically%20or%20virtually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20during%20a%20podcast%20shared%20on%20X%20on%20February%2022%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20addressed%20students%20at%20IIT%20Ranchi%20when%20someone%20hacked%20into%20the%20session%20and%20played%20pornographic%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20I%20was%20speaking%20at%20Ranchi%20IIT%20to%20several%20hundred%20students...%20and%20someone%20hacked%20in%20and%20started%20showing%20pornography%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20quickly%20flagged%20the%20claim%20as%20false%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20no%20IIT%20exists%20in%20Ranchi%20and%20that%20no%20official%20invitation%20had%20been%20extended%20to%20Mr%20Pitroda.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740722460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fk0pcivcg_sam-pitroda-pti-image-650_650x400_22_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-day-after-centres-fact-check-sam-pitrodas-big-claim-about-iit-roorkee-7813280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20Centre%20dismissed%20Congress%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20statement%20about%20an%20objectionable%20video%20being%20played%20during%20his%20webcast%20with%20%26quot%3BIIT%20Ranchi%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20made%20a%20similar%20claim%20about%20IIT%20Roorkee.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-day-after-centres-fact-che