pUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuspicious%26quot%3B%3A%20Cops%20After%20Oscar-Winner%20Gene%20Hackman%2C%20Wife%20Found%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOscar-winner%20Gene%20Hackman%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20one%20of%20their%20dogs%20were%20apparently%20dead%20for%20some%20time%20before%20a%20maintenance%20worker%20discovered%20their%20bodies%20at%20the%20couple's%20home%20in%20Santa%20Fe%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20were%20found%20Wednesday.%20Denise%20Avila%2C%20a%20sheriff's%20office%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20they%20had%20been%20shot%20or%20had%20any%20wounds%20that%20would%20indicate%20foul%20play.%20But%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20detectives%20wrote%20in%20a%20search%20warrant%20affidavit%20investigators%20thought%20the%20deaths%20were%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20enough%20in%20nature%20to%20require%20a%20thorough%20search%20and%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%2C%2095%2C%20was%20in%20an%20entryway%2C%20and%20his%2065-year-old%20wife%2C%20Betsy%20Arakawa%2C%20was%20lying%20on%20her%20right%20side%20in%20the%20bathroom.%20A%20space%20heater%20was%20next%20to%20her%20head%20and%20may%20have%20fallen%20when%20she%20abruptly%20dropped%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20according%20to%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Mexico%20Gas%20Co%20tested%20the%20gas%20lines%20in%20and%20around%20the%20home%20after%20the%20bodies%20were%20discovered%2C%20according%20to%20the%20warrant.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20didn't%20find%20any%20signs%20of%20problems%20and%20the%20Fire%20Department%20found%20no%20signs%20of%20a%20carbon%20monoxide%20leak%20or%20poisoning.%20A%20detective%20wrote%20that%20there%20were%20no%20obvious%20signs%20of%20a%20gas%20leak%2C%20but%20he%20noted%20that%20people%20exposed%20to%20gas%20leaks%20or%20carbon%20monoxide%20might%20not%20show%20signs%20of%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gruff%20but%20beloved%20Hackman%20was%20among%20the%20most%20accomplished%20actors%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20appearing%20as%20villains%2C%20heroes%20and%20antiheroes%20in%20dozens%20of%20dramas%2C%20comedies%20and%20action%20films%20from%20the%201960s%20until%20his%20retirement%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20loved%20and%20admired%20by%20millions%20around%20the%20world%20for%20his%20brilliant%20acting%20career%2C%20but%20to%20us%20he%20was%20always%20just%20Dad%20and%20Grandpa%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20daughters%20and%20granddaughter%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20miss%20him%20sorely%20and%20are%20devastated%20by%20the%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorker%20found%20bodies%20of%20Hackman%20and%20his%20wife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20search%20warrant%20affidavit%2C%20a%20maintenance%20worker%20reported%20that%20the%20home's%20front%20door%20was%20open%20when%20he%20arrived%20to%20do%20routine%20work%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20he%20called%20police%20after%20finding%20the%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20911%20call%2C%20the%20maintenance%20worker%20said%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20get%20inside%20when%20the%20operator%20asked%20whether%20the%20people%20in%20the%20house%20were%20breathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20subdivision's%20caretaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20inside%20the%20house.%20It's%20closed.%20It's%20locked.%20I%20can't%20go%20in.%20But%20I%20can%20see%20she's%20laying%20down%20on%20the%20floor%20from%20the%20window.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20another%20worker%20later%20told%20authorities%20that%20they%20rarely%20saw%20the%20homeowners%20and%20their%20last%20contact%20with%20them%20had%20been%20about%20two%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20appeared%20to%20have%20fallen%2C%20a%20deputy%20observed.%20A%20cane%20was%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dead%20German%20shepherd%20was%20found%20in%20a%20bathroom%20closet%20near%20Arakawa%2C%20police%20said.%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20Sheriff%20Adan%20Mendoza%20said%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20Thursday%20that%20the%20dog%20was%20found%20in%20a%20kennel.%20Two%20healthy%20dogs%20were%20found%20on%20the%20property%20-%20one%20inside%20and%20one%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20a%20struggle%2C%26quot%3B%20Mendoza%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20anything%20that%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20home%20or%20disturbed%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%20would%20be%20indication%20that%20there%20was%20a%20crime%20that%20had%20occurred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20of%20autopsies%20conducted%20on%20both%20bodies%20are%20not%20available%20yet%2C%20sheriff's%20officials%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20carbon%20monoxide%20and%20toxicology%20test%20results%20are%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20warrant%20affidavit%20suggests%20that%20police%20appear%20to%20have%20a%20working%20theory%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20kind%20of%20gas%20poisoning%26quot%3B%20happened%2C%20but%20that%20they%20don't%20know%20yet%20and%20aren't%20ruling%20anything%20out%2C%20Loyola%20Marymount%20University%20law%20professor%20Laurie%20Levenson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20clear%20evidence%20that%20it's%20any%20type%20of%20homicide%2C%20but%20they're%20asking%20for%20blunt%20instruments%20or%20other%20weapons%20that%20could%20be%20used%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Levenson%2C%20who%20has%20no%20connection%20to%20the%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20also%20look%20like%20some%20kind%20of%20planned%20double-suicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%20%26amp%3B%20Mary%20Law%20School%20professor%20Jeffrey%20Bellin%20said%20the%20request%20for%20a%20search%20warrant%20was%20somewhat%20unusual%20because%20investigators%20who%20file%20one%20usually%20believe%20a%20specific%20crime%20was%20committed.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20no%20alleged%20crime%20was%20mentioned%2C%20Bellin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20tend%20to%20overstate%20what%20they%20know%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20opposite%2C%20said%20Bellin%2C%20who%20also%20isn't%20tied%20to%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20struck%20me%20as%20very%20careful%20in%20a%20way%20that%20search%20warrant%20affidavits%20often%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EActor%20known%20for%20his%20versatility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20routinely%20showed%20up%20on%20Hollywood%20lists%20of%20greatest%20American%20actors%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20He%20could%20play%20virtually%20any%20kind%20of%20role%2C%20from%20comic%20book%20villain%20Lex%20Luthor%20in%20%26quot%3BSuperman%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20coach%20finding%20redemption%20in%20the%20sentimental%20favorite%20%26quot%3BHoosiers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20was%20a%20five-time%20Oscar%20nominee%20who%20won%20best%20actor%20in%20a%20leading%20role%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20French%20Connection%26quot%3B%20in%201972%20and%20best%20actor%20in%20a%20supporting%20role%20for%20%26quot%3BUnforgiven%26quot%3B%20two%20decades%20later.%20His%20death%20comes%20just%20four%20days%20before%20this%20year's%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETributes%20quickly%20poured%20in%20from%20Hollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20finer%20actor%20than%20Gene%2C%26quot%3B%20actor-director%20Clint%20Eastwood%2C%20Hackman's%20%26quot%3BUnforgiven%26quot%3B%20co-star%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIntense%20and%20instinctive.%20Never%20a%20false%20note.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20dear%20friend%20whom%20I%20will%20miss%20very%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHackman%20and%20Arakawa%20settled%20in%20Santa%20Fe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20met%20Arakawa%2C%20a%20classically%20trained%20pianist%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20when%20she%20was%20working%20part-time%20at%20a%20California%20gym%20in%20the%20mid-1980s.%20They%20soon%20moved%20in%20together%20and%20relocated%20to%20Santa%20Fe%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20Southwestern-style%20ranch%20on%20Old%20Sunset%20Trail%20sits%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20a%20gated%20community%20with%20views%20of%20the%20Rocky%20Mountains.%20The%20sprawling%20four-bedroom%20home%20on%206%20acres%20(2.4%20hectares)%20was%20built%20in%201997%20and%20had%20an%20estimated%20market%20value%20of%20a%20little%20over%20%244%20million%2C%20according%20to%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20property%20tax%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20and%20his%20wife%20also%20owned%20a%20more%20modest%20home%20next%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHackman%20also%20co-wrote%20three%20novels%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20swashbuckler%2C%20%26quot%3BWake%20of%20the%20Perdido%20Star%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20Daniel%20Lenihan%20in%201999%2C%20according%20to%20publisher%20Simon%20%26amp%3B%20Schuster.%20He%20then%20penned%20two%20by%20himself%2C%20concluding%20with%20%26quot%3BPursuit%26quot%3B%20in%202013%2C%20about%20a%20female%20police%20officer%20on%20the%20tail%20of%20a%20predator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20couple%20of%20decades%20in%20New%20Mexico%2C%20Hackman%20was%20often%20seen%20around%20the%20historic%20state%20capital%2C%20known%20as%20an%20artist%20enclave%2C%20tourism%20destination%20and%20retreat%20for%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20on%20the%20board%20of%20trustees%20for%20the%20Georgia%20O'Keeffe%20Museum%20from%201997-2004%2C%20the%20museum%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHackman's%20later%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20he%20was%20far%20less%20visible%2C%20though%20even%20the%20most%20mundane%20outings%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20press.%20There%20were%20articles%20about%20him%20attending%20a%20show%20at%20a%20performing%20arts%20center%20in%202018%2C%20as%20well%20as%20pumping%20