previous%20matches.%C2%A0Pakistan%2C%20hosting%20an%20ICC%20tournament%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2029%20years%2C%20had%20hoped%20for%20a%20strong%20finish%20but%20ended%20their%20disastrous%C2%A0campaign%C2%A0without%20a%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersistent%20downpour%20left%20the%20ground%20soaked%2C%20with%20covers%20in%20place%20and%20puddles%20forming%20around%20the%20field.%20With%20weather%20not%20improving%2C%20match%20officials%20called%20off%20the%20game%20nearly%20two%20hours%20after%20the%20scheduled%20start%20time.%20The%20gloomy%20weather%20prevented%20even%20the%20toss%20from%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20two%20teams%20shared%20one%20point%20each%2C%20though%20both%C2%A0Pakistan%C2%A0and%20Bangladesh%20finished%20the%20tournament%C2%A0winless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20match%20in%20Rawalpindi%20to%20be%20called%20off%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled%2C%20following%20the%20washout%20between%20South%20Africa%20and%20Australia%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rain-induced%20abandonment%20left%20the%20home%20fans%20frustrated%2C%20as%20they%20hoped%20for%20play%20at%20the%20Rawalpindi%20Cricket%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%C2%A0have%20faced%20criticism%20for%20their%20poor%20showing%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20having%20suffered%20defeats%20to%20New%20Zealand%20(by%2060%20runs)%20and%20India%20(by%20six%20wickets).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20do%20well%20and%20perform%20well%20in%20front%20of%20our%20nation.%20The%20expectations%20are%20very%20high.%20We%20didn't%20perform%20well%20and%20it%20is%20disappointing%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Pakistan%C2%A0captain%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20road%20ahead%2C%20Rizwan%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20learn%20from%20your%20mistakes.%20We%20have%20made%20mistakes%20in%20the%20last%20few%20games.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20next%20going%20to%20New%20Zealand%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20perform%20there%20and%20the%20mistakes%20that%20we%20did%20against%20New%20Zealand%20here%20in%C2%A0Pakistan%2C%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20that.%20And%20we%20will%20do%20better%20in%20New%20Zealand.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20ourselves%20playing%20against%20India'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20assistant%20coach%2C%20Azhar%20Mahmood%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20city%2C%20attributed%20his%20team's%20poor%20show%20in%20the%20tournament%20to%20injuries%20to%20key%20players%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20team%20took%20too%20much%20pressure%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20played%20well%20in%20this%20tournament.%20We%20have%20played%20good%20cricket%20in%20this%20format%2C%20but%20in%20the%20tournament%20it%20has%20not%20gone%20well%20because%20of%20injuries.%20Against%20India%2C%20we%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20where%20we%20need%20to%20improve.%20It%20is%20all%20about%20adapting%20and%20taking%20responsibility.%20The%20results%20have%20also%20been%20a%20surprise%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Test%20all-rounder%20said%20that%20the%20people%20need%20to%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20talent%20we%20identify%20for%20it%20to%20come%20good%20over%20the%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mahmood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%C2%A0had%20lost%20two%20top%20players%20--%20Fakhar%20Zaman%20and%20Saim%20Ayub%20--%20to%20injuries%2C%20affecting%20their%C2%A0campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guy%20who%20has%20been%20performing%20from%20the%20last%20few%20months%20in%20Australia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Zimbabwe...%20the%20team%20was%20combined%20and%20then%20suddenly%20when%20someone%20is%20injured%2C%20the%20team%20will%20be%20disturbed%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Rizwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20captain%2C%20you%20can%20look%20forward%20to%20that%20as%20well.%20One%20side%20you%20can%20say%20that%20the%20team%20is%20disturbed%2C%20but%20this%20is%20no%20excuse.%20Yes%2C%20Fakhar%20Zaman%20and%20Saim%20Ayub%20were%20injured%2C%20but%20we%20will%20learn%20from%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20captain%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20very%20disappointed.%20We%20are%20all%20here%20for%20the%20nation.%C2%A0Pakistan%C2%A0is%20our%20priority%20and%20the%20expectation%20from%20us%20is%20very%20high.%20We%20are%20upset%20and%20we%20are%20accepting%20that%20we%20didn't%20do%20well.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20will%20do%20more%20hard%20work%20and%20comeback%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Rizwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuch%20to%20reflect%20for%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%2C%20who%20also%20ended%20their%20tournament%C2%A0winless%2C%20will%20return%20home%20with%20much%20to%20reflect%20on%20after%20losing%20to%20India%20by%20six%20wickets%20and%20New%20Zealand%20by%20five%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20disappointed.%20We%20really%20wanted%20to%20play%20this%20match%2C%20but%20can't%20do%20anything%20about%20the%20weather.%20The%20way%20we%20held%20the%20game%20for%20long%20periods%20was%20very%20inspiring%20for%20us%20in%20the%20two%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20Bangladesh%20captain%2C%20Najmul%20Hossain%20Shanto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20our%20mistakes.%20We%20will%20make%20a%20proper%20plan%20and%20execute%20the%20plan.%26quot%3B%20Talking%20about%20their%20bowling%20unit%2C%20Shanto%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20struggled%20with%20our%20fast%20bowling%20unit%2C%20but%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20a%20lot%20of%20fast%20bowlers%20are%20coming%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BS