nnes-michael-jackson-mick-jagger-among-other-hollywood-stars-names-included%2Farticleshow%2F118615264.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20joins%20the%20quantum%20computing%20race%2C%20announcing%20new%20'Ocelot'%20chip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20superconducting-qubit%20quantum%20chip%20being%20wire-bonded%20to%20a%20circuit%20board%20at%20the%20AWS%20Center%20for%20Quantum%20Computing%20in%20Pasadena%2C%20Calif.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0e6a9b8b41a9673f9423e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20superconducting-qubit%20quantum%20chip%20being%20wire-bonded%20to%20a%20circuit%20board%20at%20the%20AWS%20Center%20for%20Quantum%20Computing%20in%20Pasadena%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%20on%20Thursday%20debuted%20its%20new%20quantum%20computing%20chip%2C%20a%20prototype%20called%20Ocelot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20says%20the%20Ocelot%20represents%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20error%20correction%20and%20scalability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20quantum%20computing%20field%20is%20heating%20up%20with%20recent%20advancements%20from%20Google%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20debuted%20its%20prototype%20quantum%20chip%2C%20the%20Ocelot%2C%20making%20headway%20in%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20functional%20quantum%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20makes%20Ocelot%20different%20and%20special%20is%20the%20way%20it%20approaches%20the%20fundamental%20challenge%20we%20have%20with%20quantum%20computers%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20errors%20that%20they're%20susceptible%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Oskar%20Painter%2C%20the%20director%20of%20quantum%20hardware%20at%20AWS%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%2C%20in%20research%20published%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D9a7950957287cc6c67978f6753579a62eaf40eae327a3f3164f96d77da37c4f1%26postID%3D67c0cfbe3620c014826f84bb%26postSlug%3Damazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41586-025-08642-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENature%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20Ocelot%20represents%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20error%20correction%20and%20scalability%20%E2%80%94%20two%20key%20issues%20that%20have%20long%20slowed%20advancement%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20Ocelot%20prototype%20demonstrated%20the%20potential%20to%20increase%20efficiency%20in%20quantum%20error%20correction%20by%20up%20to%2090%25%20compared%20to%20conventional%20approaches%2C%20the%20company%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20efficiency%20is%20something%20on%20the%20order%20of%20a%20factor%20of%20five%20to%2010x%20so%20it's%20a%20pretty%20significant%20reduction%2C%26quot%3B%20Painter%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20about%20a%20factor%20of%20a%20billion%20to%20reduce%20the%20error%20rate%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20that%20it's%20a%20huge%20gap%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20quantum%20error%20correction%20is%20up%20to%20the%20challenge%2C%20and%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20we%20eventually%20can%20bridge%20this%20massive%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e99ed04-d145-4b6a-afbd-2d39ed735339%5C%22%3ESchr%C3%B6dinger's%20qubits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fquantum-watch-3-quantum-computing-startups-set-to-disrupt-the-industry-1034380215%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuantum%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20growing%20field%20of%20technology%20that%20combines%20computer%20science%2C%20math%2C%20and%20quantum%20mechanics.%20It%20relies%20on%20units%20of%20information%20called%20qubits%20rather%20than%20the%20binary%20bits%20used%20in%20classical%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQubits%20hold%20more%20information%20than%20binary%20bits%20and%20can%20exist%20in%20multiple%20states%20simultaneously.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20unstable%2C%20difficult%20to%20measure%2C%20and%20require%20specific%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0such%20as%20low%20light%20or%20extremely%20cold%20environments%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20reliably%20replicate%20results%20without%20errors%2C%20which%20has%20slowed%20progress%20in%20the%20field%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20they%20behave%20predictably%20at%20a%20large%20enough%20scale%2C%20qubits%20enable%20quantum%20computers%20to%20solve%20more%20complex%20calculations%20more%20quickly%20than%20classical%20computers%20can.%20Researchers%20in%20the%20field%20agree%20that%20computations%20solvable%20through%20quantum%20computing%20could%20help%20discover%20new%20drugs%2C%20promote%20sustainable%20food%20growth%20in%20harsh%20climates%2C%20develop%20new%20chemical%20compounds%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreak%20our%20current%20encryption%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20other%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20Ocelot%20chip%20uses%20a%20kind%20of%20qubit%20technology%20called%20cat%20qubits%2C%20named%20after%20the%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-entanglement-experiment-2015-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESchr%C3%B6dinger's%20cat%3C%2Fa%3E%20thought%20experiment.%20This%20technology%20intrinsically%20suppresses%20certain%20forms%20of%20errors%2C%C2%A0simplifying%20and%20reducing%20the%20quantum%20error%20correction%20required%20to%20build%20a%20full-fledged%20quantum%20computer%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20chip%20has%20a%20unique%20architecture%20that%20integrates%20the%20cat%20qubit%20technology%20and%20additional%20quantum%20error%20correction%20components%20into%20the%20chip%20that%20can%20be%20manufactured%20using%20processes%20borrowed%20from%20the%20electronics%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298d08dfd-0794-41e9-8d40-18bd00b8f86c%5C%22%3EA%20quantum%20'tipping%20point'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20fully-fledged%20and%20functional%20quantum%20computers%20can%20become%20commercially%20useful%2C%20Painter%20and%20other%20quantum%20researchers%20agree%20they%20must%20make%20more%20progress%20in%20error%20reduction%20and%20scalability.%20While%20Amazon's%20new%20chip%20doesn't%20mean%20commercially%20useful%20quantum%20computers%20are%20in%20production%20now%2C%20it's%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20recent%20advancements%20in%20the%20field%20that%20has%20galvanized%20the%20industry%20and%20suggests%20commercial%20adoption%20will%20come%20sooner%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Schoelkopf%2C%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20scientist%20of%20Quantum%20Circuits%2C%20said%20Amazon's%20research%20results%20%26quot%3Bhighlight%20how%20more%20efficient%20error%20correction%20is%20key%20to%20ensuring%20viable%20quantum%20computing.%20%26quot%3B%20He%20described%20the%20company's%20progress%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20step%20toward%20exploring%20and%20preparing%20for%20future%20roadmaps%26quot%3B%20in%20further%20developing%20quantum%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20announcement%20comes%20about%20a%20week%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20unveiled%20its%20quantum%20chip%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMajorana%201.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Microsoft%20says%20its%20chip%C2%A0is%20powered%20by%20a%20new%20state%20of%20matter%20and%20allows%20for%20more%20stable%2C%20scalable%2C%20and%20simplified%20quantum%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%20announced%20its%20quantum%20chip%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-unveiled-quantum-computer-chip-willow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWillow%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20company%20says%20can%20perform%20a%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%20in%20under%20five%20minutes.%20It's%20a%20task%20that%20would%20take%20the%20current%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%20to%20complete%20%E2%80%94%20a%20timeframe%20that%20exceeds%20the%20age%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20are%20at%20a%20very%20exciting%20time%20in%20quantum%20computing%2C%20and%20you're%20hearing%20a%20lot%20about%20it%20because%20this%20is%20a%20real%20tipping%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Painter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c003ef6b-334b-4c1f-bb2f-26d6985621f0%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20in%20the%20lead%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESankar%20Das%20Sarma%2C%20a%20theoretical%20condensed%20matter%20physicist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland's%20Joint%20Quantum%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20Amazon's%20Ocelot%20chip%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20conventional%20superconducting%20chip%2C%20perhaps%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20developed%20by%20Google%20and%20IBM%2C%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20one%20recently%20unveiled%20by%20Microsoft%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0though%20he%20added%20it's%20too%20soon%20to%20say%20which%20company%20is%20ahead%20in%20their%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MSFT%20work%20is%20based%20on%20topological%20Majorana%20zero%20modes%2C%20which%20also%20has%20a%20superconductor%2C%20but%20in%20a%20radically%20different%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20Sarma%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIn%20particular%2C%20the%20MSFT%20device%2C%20if%20it%20works%20correctly%2C%20is%20protected%20topologically%20with%20minimal%20need%20for%20error%20correction%2C%20whereas%20the%20AWS%20claim%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20they%20have%20made%20some%20improvement%20in%20the%20conventional%20error%20correction%20schemes.%20The%20two%20approaches%20are%20very%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20the%20field%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20Amazon's%20and%20other%20companies'%20advancements%2C%20hoping%20to%20prove%20that%20quantum%20technology%20will%20become%20commercially%20viable%20sooner%20than%20anticipated.%20In%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fquantum-computing-stocks-jensen-huang-nvidia-ces-rigetti-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENvidia%20CEO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Jensen%20Huang%20suggested%20we%20were%20still%2020%20years%20away%20from%20the%20technology%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20sending%20quantum%20stocks%20tumbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroy%20Nelson%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20Lastwall%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20provider%20of%20quantum%20resilient%20technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20each%20company's%20announcement%20represents%20another%20building%20block%20that%20the%20industry%20will%20use%20along%20the%20way%20to%20a%20functioning%20quantum%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20lots%20of%20challenges%20ahead.%20What%20Amazon%20gained%20in%20error%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20has%20led%20to%20some%20new%20scientific%20knowledge%20and%20discoveries%20in%20error%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20trade-off%20for%20the%20complexity%20and%20the%20sophistication%20of%20the%20control%20systems%20and%20the%20readouts%20from%20the%20chip%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20still%20in%20prototype%20days%2C%20and%20we%20still%20have%20multiple%20years%20to%20go%2C%20but%20they've%20made%20a%20great%20leap%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740711900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0e6c8b8b41a9673f94247%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20debuted%20its%20new%20%26quot%3BOcelot%26quot%3B%20chip%2C%20joining%20other%20tech%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%20in%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20full-fledged%20quantum%20computers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan's%20MeToo%20icon%20is%20up%20for%20an%20Oscar%20-%20but%20the%20film%20can't%20air%20in%20the%20country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740711740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0aa4%2Flive%2F3be422f0-f4f0-11ef-ae0a-4bca4f518eb0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcm2j1r1qn3zo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiori%20became%20the%20face%20of%20Japan's%20MeToo%20movement%20after%20she%20accused%20a%20prominent%20journalist%20of%