s-on-trump-card-for-political-survival%2Farticleshow%2F118615584.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118615584.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBrazil's%20former%20president%20Jair%20Bolsonaro%2C%20charged%20with%20attempting%20a%20coup%20and%20barred%20from%20office%2C%20remains%20hopeful%20about%20his%20political%20future%2C%20drawing%20inspiration%20from%20US%20President%20Trump's%20comeback.%20Despite%20facing%20serious%20charges%20and%20legal%20challenges%2C%20Bolsonaro%20seeks%20support%20from%20Trump%20and%20conservative%20circles%20to%20pressure%20Brazilian%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-bolsonaro-bets-on-trump-card-for-political-survival%2Farticleshow%2F118615584.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-bolsonaro-bets-on-trump-card-for-political-survival%2Famp_articleshow%2F118615584.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-bolsonaro-bets-on-trump-card-for-political-survival%2Famp_articleshow%2F118615584.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20PM%20Under%20Pressure%20Over%20CT%202025%2C%20Asked%20To%20Take%20Up%20Matter%20In%20Parliament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Pakistan%20government%20official%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20request%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20country's%20cricket%20team's%20disappointing%20performance%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Parliament%20and%20the%20Federal%20Cabinet.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20(Pakistan)%20Cricket%20Board%20is%20an%20independent%20institution.%20They%20can%20do%20as%20they%20please%2C%20which%20they%20have.%20And%20what%20they've%20done%2C%20I%20will%20request%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20and%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20Sanaullah%2C%20the%20advisor%20to%20the%20PM%20on%20Political%20and%20Public%20Affairs%2C%20told%20Geo%20TV%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHosts%20Pakistan's%20campaign%20in%20the%20marquee%20tournament%20ended%20prematurely%20with%20big%20defeats%20to%20New%20Zealand%20(by%2060%20runs)%20and%20India%20(by%20six%20wickets).%20Their%20inconsequential%20last%20group%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20Rawalpindi%20was%20called%20off%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled%20due%20to%20incessant%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanaullah%2C%20a%20former%20federal%20and%20provincial%20minister%2C%20and%20a%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20ruling%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20party%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20caretaker%20government%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20last%20year%20had%20completely%20detached%20the%20PCB%20from%20the%20Federal%20Government's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20we%20have%20been%20facing%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20cricket%20and%20changes%20in%20the%20Board%20for%20the%20past%20decade%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanaullah%2C%20while%20also%20highlighting%20the%20dismal%20condition%20of%20the%20sport%20at%20the%20club%2C%20university%20and%20district%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20make%20PCB%20accountable%20for%20the%20money%20spent%20at%20a%20time%20when%20conditions%20at%20the%20grassroots%20and%20club%20level%20remained%20dismal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20expenditure%20happening%20at%20a%20higher%20level%20(PCB)%20should%20be%20brought%20in%20front%20of%20the%20country%20and%20Parliament.%20Mentors%20are%20being%20paid%20five%20million%20rupees%20and%20they%20have%20been%20heard%20admitting%20in%20the%20media%20that%20they%20are%20unaware%20of%20their%20responsibilities...%20so%20they've%20been%20taking%20money%20for%20not%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20the%20perks%20and%20privileges%20of%20the%20PCB%20to%20players%20and%20officials%2C%20you'll%20wonder%20if%20this%20is%20Pakistan%20or%20some%20progressive%20European%20nation.%20These%20are%20things%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20himself%20will%20take%20notice%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20process%20that%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20a%20while%20where%20people%20of%20their%20own%20wish%20take%20up%20positions%20(in%20the%20PCB)%20and%20do%20as%20they%20please%2C%20which%20then%20leads%20to%20the%20current%20conditions%20of%20cricket%20and%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20needs%20to%20be%20improvement%2C%20and%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20system%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20stable%20board%20like%20there%20is%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740710640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F92iu6qp8_shehbaz-sharif_625x300_24_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwill-request-pm-sharif-to-take-up-pak-team-debacle-in-parliament-senior-govt-official-7809972%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hosts%20Pakistan's%20campaign%20in%20the%20marquee%20tournament%20ended%20prematurely%20with%20big%20defeats%20to%20New%20Zealand%20(by%2060%20runs)%20and%20India%20(by%20six%20wickets).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwill-request-pm-sharif-to-take-up-pak-team-debacle-in-parliament-senior-govt-official-7809972%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sean%20%E2%80%98Diddy%E2%80%99%20Combs%