%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fstudents-who-led-anti-hasina-protests-to-launch-party-today%2Famp_articleshow%2F118615163.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Authority%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20Judge%20Halts%20Donald%20Trump's%20Mass%20Firing%20Of%20Federal%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20on%20Thursday%20ordered%20the%20US%20government%20to%20reverse%20mass%20firings%20that%20are%20part%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk's%20plan%20to%20slash%20the%20government's%20workforce%2C%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20directs%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20to%20withdraw%20directives%20sent%20to%20a%20number%20of%20federal%20agencies%20that%20resulted%20in%20thousands%20of%20staff%20being%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20does%20not%20have%20any%20authority%20whatsoever%20under%20any%20statute%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20universe%20to%20hire%20and%20fire%20employees%20at%20another%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20District%20Judge%20William%20Alsup%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20given%20the%20authority%20to%20hire%20and%20fire%20to%20the%20agencies%20themselves.%20The%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20statutory%20authority%20to%20hire%20and%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20federal%20court%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20is%20the%20latest%20legal%20blow%20to%20Trump's%20efforts%20to%20bring%20the%20US%20government%20to%20heel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20days%20after%20another%20district%20judge%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%20blocked%20his%20ban%20on%20refugee%20admissions%2C%20and%20weeks%20after%20a%20court%20suspended%20his%20executive%20order%20overturning%20the%20constitutional%20guarantee%20of%20birthright%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20ruling%20ca