erdine%20University%20said%20that%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment's%20%26quot%3Bimproper%20use%20of%20the%20asserted%20trademarks%26quot%3B%20could%20%26quot%3Bdilute%2C%20tarnish%2C%20and%20disparage%20Pepperdine's%20reputation%20and%20marks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParticularly%20because%20the%20Netflix%20show%20has%20content%20that%20is%20so%20at%20odds%20with%20Pepperdine's%20conservative%20values%20and%20religious%20philosophy%2C%20it%20might%20harm%20Pepperdine's%20mark%20in%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeltz%20said%20the%20trademark%20dilution%20claim%20requires%20proof%20of%20fame%2C%20which%20would%20examine%20whether%20Pepperdine%20University's%20trademarks%20are%20well-known%20and%20being%20diluted%20by%20%26quot%3BRunning%20Point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261b072e1-6ecb-4f58-ae23-289ad9a829c3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20judge%20denied%20the%20university's%20TRO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20granted%2C%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20against%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Entertainment%20would%20have%20barred%20them%20from%20certain%20actions%2C%20including%20airing%20%26quot%3BRunning%20Point%26quot%3B%20episodes%20unless%20they're%20first%20edited%20to%20exclude%20references%20to%20the%20fictitious%20Waves%20team%20and%20the%20university's%20trademarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20on%20Monday%2C%20Netflix%20argued%20against%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%2C%20saying%20the%20use%20of%20Waves%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bexplicitly%20misleading%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20use%20is%20%26quot%3Bartistically%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20among%20other%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20denied%20Pepperdine%20University's%20request%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222513%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pepperdine%20University%20Waves'%20mascot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0a602b8b41