oduced%C2%A011.61%20lakh%20tonnes%C2%A0of%20turmeric%20making%20it%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producer%2C%20consumer%2C%20and%20exporter.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201998%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20local%20variety%2C%20Kadja%2C%20and%20observed%20a%20few%20plants%20that%20were%20early%20maturing%20and%20possessed%20good%20vigour.%20I%20harvested%20the%20produce%20from%20these%20plants%20and%20selected%20the%20ones%20untouched%20by%20disease%2C%20had%20bigger%20rhizomes%2C%20were%20bright%20in%20colour%20and%20high-yielding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karekar%2C%20who%20introduces%20himself%20as%20%E2%80%9C12%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20fail%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20has%20been%20growing%20turmeric%20as%20an%20intercrop%20between%20the%20500%20areca%20nut%20palms%2C%20and%2050%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354850%2Fhomemaker-entrepreneur-organic-coconut-greenaura-oil-pickles-business-kerala-sumila-jayaraj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut%20palms%3C%2Fa%3E%20standing%20on%20his%20family%20farm%20since%20the%20age%20of%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20call%20it%20SK-4%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20Karekar%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20superior%20clone%20with%20all%20the%20desired%20traits%20and%20named%20it%20SK-4%2C%20taking%20the%20first%20letter%20of%20Shendge%20Kaka%2C%20the%20farmer%20who%20initially%20gave%20him%20tubers%20of%20Sangli%20Kadapa%20variety%2C%20Special%20Konkan%2C%20and%20his%20own%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202020%20Kharif%20season%2C%20the%20Dapoli-based%20Dr%20Balasaheb%20Sawant%20Konkan%20Krishi%20Vidyapeeth%20(DBSKKV)%20