40635839-150x68.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20stands%20beside%20a%20harvest%20of%20the%20SK-4%20turmeric%20variety%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20trials%20were%20spread%20over%20two%20years%20and%20we%20found%20that%20SK-4%20was%20characterised%20by%20its%20high%20yield%20potential%2C%20like%20Rajendra%20Sona.%20The%20latter%E2%80%99s%20seed%20material%20is%20always%20scarce%20and%20we%20hope%20the%20new%20variety%20will%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20SK-4%20is%20a%20good%20alternative%20for%20those%20growing%20it%20in%20Konkan%E2%80%99s%20high-rainfall%20region.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20evaluated%20in%20low%20rainfall%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Prafulla%20Mali%2C%20horticulturist%2C%20DBSKKV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHigh%20curcumin%20content%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20variety%20possesses%20an%20attractive%20bright%20reddish-yellow%20colour%20and%20has%20big-sized%20rhizomes.%20It%20is%20a%20short%20duration%20(160-170%20days)%20variety%20suitable%20for%20high%20rainfall%20regions%20and%20with%20good%20tolerance%20to%20%3Cem%3Ekarpa%20(%3C%2Fem%3Erhizome%20rot%20disease).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20possesses%20a%20curcumin%20content%20of%204%20per%20cent.%20For%20comparison%2C%20the%20premium-yielding%20Rajapuri%20Salem%20variety%20yields%20315.29g%20fresh%20rhizome%20per%20plant%20with%20a%20curcumin%20content%20of%203.5%20per%20cent%20and%20output%20of%2032.67t%2Fha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20farmers%20in%20Sindhudurg%20and%20Raigad%20districts%2C%20along%20with%20Ratnagiri%20are%20presently%20cultivating%20this%20variety.%20One%20Vishram%20Mali%20(58)%20of%20Velamb%20village%20in%20Guhagar%20taluka%20achieved%20the%20highest%20output%20last%20year%3A%20turmeric%20pods%20weighing%208.15%20kg%20from%20one%20sapling!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FKarekar-in-yellow-shirt-with-farmers--1740633577.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20and%20other%20turmeric%20farmers%20discuss%20the%20SK-4%20variety%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FKarekar-in-yellow-shirt-with-farmers--1740633577.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FKarekar-in-yellow-shirt-with-farmers--1740633577-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FKarekar-in-yellow-shirt-with-farmers--1740633577-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FKarekar-in-yellow-shirt-with-farmers--1740633577-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22405%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20and%20other%20turmeric%20farmers%20discuss%20the%20SK-4%20variety%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20agronomic%20practices%20for%20cultivating%20the%20SK-4%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rhizomes%20or%20fingers%20are%20planted%20in%20nursery%20bags%20in%20April%2C%20and%20by%20June%20they%20are%20transplanted%20on%20fields%20prepared%20with%20organic%20fertiliser.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20saplings%20are%20fed%20a%20second%20dose%20of%20water-soluble%20fertiliser.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crop%20is%20irrigated%20till%20January%20and%20harvested%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%2C%20with%20each%20sapling%20yielding%203.2%20kg%20or%20more.%20He%20has%20been%20propagating%20the%20variety%20for%20ten%20years%20now%20and%20regularly%20imparts%C2%A0training%20on%20plantation%20management%20to%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20the%20rhizomes%20in%20nursery%20bags%20rather%20than%20planting%20them%20directly%20on%20the%20field%20offers%2090%20per%20cent%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20farmer%20Gajendra%20Paunikar%20(55)%20of%20Nigundan%20village%2C%20who%20was%2C%20till%20very%20recently%2C%20the%20Agriculture%20Extension%20Officer%2C%20Panchayat%20Samiti%2C%20Guhagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrown%20in%2013%20states%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20NIF%20event%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20farmers%20from%20Nandurbar%2C%20Vidarbha%20along%20with%20farmers%20from%2013%20states%20bought%20tubers%20of%20the%20SK-4%20variety%20for%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Protection%20of%20Plant%20Varieties%20%26amp%3B%20Farmers%20Rights%20Authority%20(PPV%26amp%3BFRA)%20granted%20to%20SK-4%20last%20December%2C%20Kachekar%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplant%20breeder%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20the%20exclusive%20right%20to%20produce%20and%20sell%20the%20variety%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%2